{"tid":1900591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10萬隻支那鴨部隊展開部署 最快下半年前往巴基斯坦消滅蝗蟲","createTime":"2020-02-27T10:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T11:30:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"192b9616154f12341732f189549813a206726241","tid":1900591,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4446847/xl/d78c97b457031c6dc7dce12567da7426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4446847%2Fxl%2Fd78c97b457031c6dc7dce12567da7426.jpg&h=6abfd011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在非洲肆虐的蝗蟲大軍，已經一路擴展到中東的巴基斯坦、印度等地，巴基斯坦因蝗災宣佈國家進入緊急狀態，鄰近的中國已先枕戈待旦，預計部署 10 萬隻「寧波鴨」大軍前往巴基斯坦，對抗威脅區域糧食安全的大批食草害蟲。<br />\n<br />\n據《彭博》報導，浙江省農業科學院資深研究員盧立志表示，預計最早將於今年下半年將有 10 萬隻鴨子被運抵巴基斯坦，以應對沙漠蝗蟲的危害。盧立志形容，鴨子是「生物武器」，比農藥更有效。<br />\n<br />\n盧立志指出，一隻雞一天能吃掉 70 隻蝗蟲，一隻鴨子則能吃掉 200 多隻，擁有三倍作戰能力。而且鴨子吃蝗蟲完全是地毯式搜捕，連蝗蟲的蛹都不會放過，放一隻鴨子等於滅掉蝗蟲全家。<br />\n<br />\n大陸媒體《寧波晚報》稱這批鴨子大軍為「國紹 1 號」，預計鴨隻將先送往新彊展開實驗，然後再送至巴基斯坦。<br />\n<br />\n盧立志表示，浙江的紹興鴨是滅蝗界的奇才，在 2000 年時，新彊出現大批蝗蟲，但新彊人很少養鴨，因此由浙江分 10 多次空運「鴨兵」出擊，而於當年 8 月徹底殲滅蝗蟲大軍。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐喀拉蚩總領事館網站上發布的一篇報導指出，一群中國農業專家本週訪問了巴基斯坦，研究如何防堵蝗蟲繼續向東轉移。<br />\n<br />\n盧立志指出，派遣「鴨兵」出征看似簡單，但仍需要估算時機，知道何時向巴基斯坦派送鴨曲最合適，以達到最好的滅蝗效果。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，由於受災嚴重，巴基斯坦政府敦促公民也吃蝗蟲。據當地一家報紙報導，人們應該利用這種情況，選擇燒烤或咖哩蝗蟲。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國糧食及農業組織說，與非洲東部沙漠蝗蟲對抗的費用已經翻了一倍，達到 1.28 億美元，每天都有更多的國家受到影響。"},{"pid":"34847e71c6deac0399d7dc4462ea83e99ee97b0f","tid":1900591,"uid":180188,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:06:38.000Z","msg":"我以為係戰狼唔驚d fd點會估錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725b21e3316385532d737f30b6275832d3e13160","tid":1900591,"uid":300435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"9月參選人立刻發動及宣傳政綱,削減驚方預算,慳返果D錢派比市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdtdPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdtdPS</a><br />\n<br />\n既然777無恥派錢,<br />\n我地都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻宣傳政綱,<br />\n9月立會一過半,<br />\n就即刻發動議案,<br />\n削減驚方預算，<br />\n<br />\n驚方1年預算258億元,<br />\n削減一半就130億元,<br />\n4年立法任期就520億元,<br />\n再叫政府比D錢來,<br />\n就儲夠710億,<br />\n下年又可以派一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df6e9a91426a6beb9ecfdb0750f408bb5a4e200","tid":1900591,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"連蝗蟲的蛹都不會放過<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲有蛹架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ff5b184f227c357cd230515d25f11d468b4e3f","tid":1900591,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:08:52.000Z","msg":"派10萬隻支那豬過去即刻消滅蝗蟲啦<br />\n大蝗食小蝗"},{"pid":"c32cc99210c93de75f5a9b24aea3fa6de3f24c56","tid":1900591,"uid":7484,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:13:14.000Z","msg":"d 鴨 會係運送途中 直接轉去家禽市場賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06056e8af87dd25e5afa3d3a79c57e42766640ce","tid":1900591,"uid":62314,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"一陣又唔知傳播咩病毒，生態圈呢d野真係唔好亂黎"},{"pid":"ad0eb74c25bd697ad3d8c99195da2d5f956a19a6","tid":1900591,"uid":18283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"啲鴨會唔會爆炸.."},{"pid":"42fa9d88aab83b3b8f4625dd5a75d20667afd9ed","tid":1900591,"uid":4139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:20:39.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d698d11662df143789f2f8ef57c289a730b3acd","tid":1900591,"uid":104833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"鴨役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c2784f595c061d7c2d9a82d99245e4554aaeee","tid":1900591,"uid":46077,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/44ncChd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F44ncChd.png&h=935b8ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8g5cQz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8g5cQz.png&h=66d843dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfYbSQA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkfYbSQA.png&h=3e87e8e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed4e3ab737af1c1939524ece7a4b9a608900fc93","tid":1900591,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:23:26.000Z","msg":"禽流感go go go"},{"pid":"40f6459eca23a5fad561c8964193fff1312a27dd","tid":1900591,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3df6e9a91426a6beb9ecfdb0750f408bb5a4e200","tid":1900591,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"連蝗蟲的蛹都不會放過<br />\n<br />\n蝗蟲有蛹架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"冇！強國只係識食，有撚生態學知識咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/goQJJYT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t